    <title>nvm 介紹</title>
    <link href="http://allem40306.github.io/blog/posts/c414/"/>
    <id>http://allem40306.github.io/blog/posts/c414/</id>
    <published>2021-07-18T23:13:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-18T15:17:02.877Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我在一台 server 上安裝 nodejs,為了避免和其他人安裝的版本衝突，我改安裝 nvm，安裝指令如下：</p><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.38.0/install.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.38.0/install.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安裝完成，本機的 profile 會增加以下字句：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export NVM_DIR=&quot;$([ -z &quot;$&#123;XDG_CONFIG_HOME-&#125;&quot; ] &amp;&amp; printf %s &quot;$&#123;HOME&#125;/.nvm&quot; || printf %s &quot;$&#123;XDG_CONFIG_HOME&#125;/nvm&quot;)&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[ -s &quot;$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh&quot; ] &amp;&amp; \. &quot;$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh&quot; # This loads nvm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>輸入 <code>command -v nvm</code> 判斷是否安裝完成。</p><p>以下為基本指令：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvm install &lt;version&gt; # 安裝特定版本</span><br><span class="line">nvm uninstall &lt;version&gt; # 解除安裝特定版本</span><br><span class="line">nvm use &lt;version&gt; # 使用特定版本</span><br><span class="line">nvm ls # 列出畚箕已安裝的版本</span><br><span class="line">nvm ls-remote # 列出遠端所有可用的版本</span><br><span class="line">nvm --version # 查看 nvm 版本</span><br><span class="line">nvm alias &lt;name&gt; &lt;version&gt; # 將版本取別名</span><br><span class="line">nvm which &lt;version&gt; # 查看版本安裝路徑</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>參考：</p><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm</a></li><li><a href="https://pjchender.dev/nodejs/nvm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pjchender.dev/nodejs/nvm/</a></li><li><a href="https://titangene.github.io/article/nvm.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://titangene.github.io/article/nvm.html</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
